ogy, representing key themes of sacrifice, atonement, and the new covenant between God and humanity.\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4835}, {\"ngram\": \"the cornerstone\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4854}, {\"ngram\": \"Christian theology\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4876}, {\"ngram\": \"key themes\", \"from\": 4891, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"sacrifice\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4914}, {\"ngram\": \"atonement\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4925}, {\"ngram\": \"the new covenant\", \"from\": 4931, \"to\": 4947}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 4959}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 4972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has inspired countless theological reflections, liturgical practices, and artistic representations, underscoring its centrality to Christian faith and worship.\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 5136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5108, \"end\": 5117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999993888196, \"rank\": 6.113385371514655e-10, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"countless theological reflections\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 5023}, {\"ngram\": \"liturgical practices\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic representations\", \"from\": 5051, \"to\": 5075}, {\"ngram\": \"its centrality\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5104}, {\"ngram\": \"worship\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cultural and religious contexts of these events are distinct.\", \"from\": 5138, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cultural and religious contexts\", \"from\": 5138, \"to\": 5173}, {\"ngram\": \"these events\", \"from\": 5177, \"to\": 5189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The divine dinner is part of Greek mythology, a rich tapestry of sto